      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Constructs assembled from production-representative hardware. Dimensional inspection confirmed constructs within engineering tolerances. Test sample level 3 achieved, exceeding the required level 2."
