      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted under a single test condition (room temperature, quasi-static loading at 5 mm/min per ASTM F1717). Variation in loading rate or temperature was not explored. Test conditions level 1 achieved, below the required level 2. This shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given that F1717 is a standardized protocol and the COU is limited to the standard test condition."
