      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) compared using both percent difference and validation metric E/uval incorporating experimental and numerical uncertainty. All E/uval < 1.96. Output comparison level 3 achieved."
