    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted because the COU is explicitly scoped to the ASTM F1717 standard test condition and no extrapolation beyond that condition is claimed. The overall evidence package is judged sufficient to support the medium assurance level for a Class II device with medium model influence and medium decision consequence. The FEA framework is accepted for use in the regulatory submission.",
